{
    "type": "script",
    "id": "618854f1-7ed9-4746-8b2f-538c33c86c73",
    "name": "Dining Hall Ifetaya: HowtoTalkDuppy",
    "sceneId": "bf8b9872-cbdd-47c6-997c-1cd3ad91bc1e",
    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
    "trigger": {
        "type": "triggers.manual",
        "name": "Manual"
    },
    "entryPoints": [
        {
            "type": "scripts.entryPoint",
            "id": "7d476d1b-428a-48ca-b608-9b5313839560",
            "name": "Main",
            "nodes": [
                {
                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                    "id": "737d91b5-3397-41c3-99c4-a03a48015e8d",
                    "options": [
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "e5573a30-d54f-41de-91cd-76b8a962de7e",
                            "text": "Ask About Duppies",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "cf384289-bf45-46fe-aad3-f7aadbbe59f2",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "text": "What's a Duppy?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0",
                                    "notes": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "0d05976e-14c5-44aa-9301-bec0f3347e18",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Duppies are the spirits of the Dead. The ones in the castle, they are not dangerous. They just have something that troubles their souls so that they cannot find peace.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0",
                                    "notes": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "79969784-a0ca-47aa-ba74-b2d335c892c3",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "But some Duppies, they are so full of spite and ill-will that they want to destroy the Living. You best stay far away from the bad Duppies. It takes much Magic to deal with bad Duppies.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0",
                                    "notes": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                                    "id": "441de652-92b7-442b-ab20-c7af8898e491",
                                    "options": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "c77034a0-8a24-4a85-8127-b6a47893384c",
                                            "text": "Ask About Magic",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "f3d97be9-27ff-4915-b4af-3468890f4e48",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                                    "text": "What kind of magic is used against Duppies?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0",
                                                    "notes": ""
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "a97a0c88-fa32-41f9-bcde-72ddc6203330",
                                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "My people, they mostly set out protections to keep the bad Duppies at bay. They find ways to appease the bad Duppies and send them back to the Grey Lands.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0",
                                                    "notes": ""
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "2ae992f7-1247-4f57-ab53-7c4b7d4b9d7e",
                                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Here though, the Wizards make magical runes. They have runes that Duppies cannot cross. They have runes that stop a Duppy's magic. They have runes that tear apart a Duppy's spirit.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0",
                                                    "notes": ""
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "4b32ca60-5dbf-4c56-8581-c2112ea1b899",
                                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "If you want to know how to use Wizard Magic, you need to take a Wizard class. If you just want a few protective runes, you should be speaking with Mister Gregor at the store.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0",
                                                    "notes": ""
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "8",
                                            "ExitMenu": false,
                                            "notes": ""
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "cf86728f-df44-470b-9fb1-885f830b46ba",
                                            "text": "Ask About Bad Duppies",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "e97be63e-66de-4270-b654-017df7fef071",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                                    "text": "Why are some Duppies bad?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0",
                                                    "notes": ""
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "a87fc856-b7d5-47fc-afce-142237ad68d2",
                                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "Why are some people bad? People who are bad when living will be even worse when dying. All their anger, their envy, their jealousy, it festers their soul. What little good they once had in life is lost.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0",
                                                    "notes": ""
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "3",
                                            "ExitMenu": false,
                                            "notes": ""
                                        },
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "5df70ac9-8406-4969-bda0-c83e16f387b1",
                                            "text": "Ask About Ghost Dogs",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "f9344773-7fb4-4b68-a049-1f527240cbea",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                                    "text": "Why would a dog become a ghost?",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0",
                                                    "notes": ""
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "d2c56a6e-9937-4a63-a516-8ff0001c0895",
                                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "With cats, when they die, most are so full of curiosity that they go to the Grey Lands to see what they can see. Now some dogs, they are so full of loyalty, they rather stay and protect the ones they love.",
                                                    "emotion": "1",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0",
                                                    "notes": ""
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "7179979f-54bf-412f-8eb2-e0f867085dc9",
                                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "text": "The dog Duppies are here all the time, you just can't always see them. They scare the bad Duppies away.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0",
                                                    "notes": ""
                                                }
                                            ],
                                            "expression": null,
                                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                                            "minutes": "6",
                                            "ExitMenu": false,
                                            "notes": ""
                                        }
                                    ],
                                    "AutoAddDone": true,
                                    "Unique": false
                                }
                            ],
                            "expression": null,
                            "ignoreChildAvailability": false,
                            "minutes": "6",
                            "ExitMenu": false,
                            "notes": ""
                        },
                        {
                            "type": "options.text",
                            "id": "d7f8b378-4be1-4795-8d67-cf565e9a8521",
                            "text": "Ask About Talking to the Dead",
                            "nodes": [
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "d9e42eaf-2628-46e8-9fb8-78b594981f51",
                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "text": "How can I speak with ghosts?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0",
                                    "notes": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "5ac34223-c18f-42e5-8ca3-3dc68a7c4a0f",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "Ah, anyone can be speaking to ghosts! The listening part, that be harder. To most people, the voice of a Duppy is like the wind wailing in a storm.",
                                    "emotion": "1",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0",
                                    "notes": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "f5bf65d1-85f5-4740-bb8b-f64d6066580f",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "To understand what the Duppies say, you will need a magical charm or a magical spell. I can make you a gris-gris Duppy charm, if you truly want to be speaking with them.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0",
                                    "notes": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "00930c3d-ea2f-4caf-855a-15166b362dbc",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "This you must first know - to speak with the Dead, you must touch the Dead. Every touch you make, some of your life force be drawn away. Too much talking, and you will be entering the Grey Lands, too.",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "4",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0",
                                    "notes": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                    "id": "31ef01f7-a4cb-43af-9168-72014bf7f157",
                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                    "actorId2": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                    "text": "So answer me this, Mister Shawn O'Conner - do you truly wish to speak with the Dead?",
                                    "emotion": "0",
                                    "emotion2": "0",
                                    "device": "0",
                                    "device2": "0",
                                    "notes": ""
                                },
                                {
                                    "type": "nodes.showMenu",
                                    "id": "722d574e-c2b7-45f6-938d-65326207205c",
                                    "options": [
                                        {
                                            "type": "options.text",
                                            "id": "8674fe2a-1eb8-43b1-9ca3-f5039c0a96cb",
                                            "text": "Agree to Speak",
                                            "nodes": [
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "34247717-518e-49c4-9b60-47f840d5cfe9",
                                                    "actorId": "30ee2636-15e3-452e-a2db-09cbb9012970",
                                                    "actorId2": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                                    "text": "Yes, I'd like to be able to speak with the Dead.",
                                                    "emotion": "0",
                                                    "emotion2": "1",
                                                    "device": "0",
                                                    "device2": "0",
                                                    "notes": ""
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.changeReputation",
                                                    "id": "4d6f6c07-af0a-4b8e-bb0a-98ec87084e70",
                                                    "actorId": "a0b548d6-b820-451f-9508-8fc7fcf166bd",
                                                    "amount": "15",
                                                    "change": "1",
                                                    "notify": true
                                                },
                                                {
                                                    "type": "nodes.speak",
                                                    "id": "7177d907-62dc-4821-8846-5695427b4060",
